$ Python library: healpy

→ https://healpy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/[healpy] is a Python library to work with the → development/Data/geo#todo-healpix-pro[HEALpix projection].

sa:
  The python library → https://github.com/ntessore/healpix[healpix] provides functions that deal with the discretisation of the sphere itself.
  -
  It is not meant to be a replacement of healpy, and does not contain things such as functions for the visualisation of maps, or spherical harmonic transforms.
